    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "startTime": 2.7666668693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、琴乃。他のみんなはもう出かけたけど\n琴乃はどこにも行かないのか？",
      "startTime": 9.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.8999999801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それなんですけど……最近、時間があれば練習するか\n仕事のことを考えてばかりだったので",
      "startTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "空いた時間が出来て、何をやってもいいと言われると\n……何をやっていいか、分からないんです",
      "startTime": 24.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3999990899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるよ。BIG4になって以来\nますます忙しくなったからな",
      "startTime": 31.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、悩んでたら遙子さんが言ってくれたんです\n何かをしようとするんじゃなくて、のんびりすればって",
      "startTime": 38.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.133332169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いざのんびりしようとしたら\n……何をすればいいのか思いつかなくて",
      "startTime": 46.8333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7666682998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん……\nどうしたらのんびり出来るんでしょう？",
      "startTime": 53.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.8000016331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なかなか難しい質問だが……そうだな\nまずは仕事のことを、すっかり忘れてみよう",
      "startTime": 63.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "仕事のことを、忘れる……ですか？",
      "startTime": 66.6666682998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、常に仕事のことを考えてしまうって言ったよな\nそれをやめたらのんびり出来るんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 76.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8333349664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、やってみます！\n考えない考えない考えない…………",
      "startTime": 82.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6000016331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "…………ダメでした。考えないようにすると\nさらに仕事のことばかり浮かんできちゃいます",
      "startTime": 94.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。なら『忘れる』じゃなくて\n『禁止』にしてみよう",
      "startTime": 102.3000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0666682998
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今日一日、仕事のことを考えるのは一切禁止だ\n欲望のままに、してみたいことをするんだ",
      "startTime": 108.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "欲望のまま……！？　な、なんだかいけないこと\nしてるみたいです……いいんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 115.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4000051934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ちょっと新鮮かも……一日だけの不良……ワル\nふふ、ふふふふふふふふ……",
      "startTime": 126.9999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 134.6333318074
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.6333364923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ？　別に、悪いことをしろって訳じゃ\nないからな？　おい、待て、どこに行くんだ！",
      "startTime": 134.4333318074,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gamecenter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.338018300003,
          "startTime": 139.1666698257
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.338018300003,
          "startTime": 139.1666698257
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9166698257
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9166698257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（突然飛び出すから、心配してついて来たら）\n（まさか旅館の地下のゲームセンターとは……）",
      "startTime": 143.5666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、なんで悪いことをするのに\nゲームセンターなんだ？　って顔してますね",
      "startTime": 150.6333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.6000051935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃？　俺は悪いことをしようなんて言ってないぞ？\nしてみたいことをしようって言っただけなんだが",
      "startTime": 158.833333842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく慰安旅行で山梨に来たのに、観光にも行かずに\nゲームセンターで遊ぶなんて……",
      "startTime": 166.1000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.5000133316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、かなりのワルじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 168.5000133316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.166678981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか？　俺にはちょっと分からないけど……",
      "startTime": 172.166678981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.0666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、ぜーったいワルです\nあっ！　{user}さん、見て下さい！",
      "startTime": 181.0666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_52_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "おっきな恐竜が口から何か吐き出してますよ\n善は急げです、行ってみましょう！",
      "startTime": 187.9333307903,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3099.9999999000065,
          "startTime": 191.0333307902
        }
      ]
    },
    {
